snippet.title: Magitek VR : PCVR Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY NOW!
►Quest (App Lab) : https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/5555282407825417/
►PCVR (Steam):  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1745280/Magitek_VR/ 

Join our Discord
► https://discord.gg/EQ3PadmC2Z

Back us on Patreon for more early access content
► https://www.patreon.com/magitekvr

Magitek VR is a magic adventure game that uses physics driven spells based on the four elements. Use magic to fight enemies and solve puzzles as you explore the world of Embra.
